WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:10.040
Yeah that's been one of the things that I really loved is that

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:12.670
We kind of learned so many things about it's not

00:00:12.670 --> 00:00:15.220
Just the physical practice and there's so much more

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:18.240
I was expecting to come in and learn yoga and meditation, but

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:20.560
It was like really truly learning what yoga was

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:26.400
And there's not like something that I haven't taken into my real life

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.000
And I feel like the decisions that I've been making recently

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.660
Have been like the right decisions and I've been learning to trust my intuition more

00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:38.860
I'm able to just stay in a better frame of mind

00:00:38.860 --> 00:00:42.860
In the way that I approach people and having more compassion

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:46.880
How to take things and just enjoy life and every moment

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:51.400
I think that I really learned to kind of listen to my inner voice more

00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:55.960
Than the things that are around me and kind of conditioned me

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:59.160
Love yourself. It's ok not to be perfect

00:01:00.020 --> 00:01:04.100
And that's something that I was working on coming into this for a few months

00:01:04.480 --> 00:01:09.740
But being here and everything that I learned really solidified that

00:01:09.740 --> 00:01:12.000
Also being more patient with myself

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.159
And how the bad things are actually good things because

00:01:15.160 --> 00:01:20.380
You learn from them and there's lessons in every second of your life

00:01:20.380 --> 00:01:24.820
You really get to understand how powerful what you're doing in here really is

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:29.460
I mean yoga can be like this one thing that everybody benefits from

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:32.439
People say yoga and it's like anyone can do yoga

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:34.360
You just do it the right way for you

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:38.440
With yoga you can give somebody an experience

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:41.040
And at the end of class when they open up their eyes

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:45.600
You can tell that you've impacted them and

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:50.220
That they feel good at the end and you see that you've made that impact

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:54.260
So that's a great feeling too of knowing that I have this now forever

00:01:54.260 --> 00:01:56.469
Everything I've learned I've been able to use it

00:01:56.469 --> 00:02:00.860
Outside and be able to share that with others too

00:02:00.860 --> 00:02:05.820
And just it's made my life so much better in every way

